fields.name: Under Armour Sport Bras UA HeatGear High
fields.description:
No doubling up. No pinching. No slipping. Just a held-in feel, smooth, adjustable straps you slide and secure with a hook, and the sweat-wicking power of HeatGear. It's a compression bra you can actually go hard in.
 Delivers strategic support, tailored for high-support activities like running, court sports, field sports and aerobics
 Smooth, soft spacer fabric on front for support & coverage with a compression feel
 Mesh back & sides for ultimate breathability
 Quick & easy adjusts on front of straps for a custom fit
 Open keyhole back design for easy on/off
 Elastic band feels super-smooth & soft
Care & Material

fields.name: adidas Originals Ribbed Leggings
fields.description:
Product InfoReviewDeliveryReturns
Level up your comfort with these women's Ribbed Leggings from adidas Originals. In a Black colourway, these slim fit leggings are cut from light, stretchy fabric, a minimum of 70% of which is made using recycled material, for easy comfort. They feature an elasticated waistband for a relaxed wear and are finished up with signature Trefoil branding to the leg.

fields.name: adidas Originals Floral 3-Stripes Leggings
fields.description: Refresh your staple cuts with these women's Floral 3-Stripes Leggings from adidas Originals. In a Black colourway, these slim-fit leggings are made with a super-soft stretch cotton for lasting comfort. They feature a high-rise, deep elasticated waistband for a snug, secure fit, and are finished with floral print 3-Stripes down the sides. Signed off with the iconic adidas Originals Trefoil logo to the back waist.

fields.name: Calvin Klein Underwear Modern Cotton Bikini Briefs
fields.description: Give your underwear an update with these women's Modern Cotton Briefs from Calvin Klein. With a stretchy feel for effortless comfort, they're cut from a soft cotton-modal blend in a Grey colourway. Featuring a mid-rise cut and a woven, elasticated waistband, they're finished with iconic Calvin Klein branding. Please note: For hygiene reasons, underwear cannot be returned.

fields.name: Nike Free Metcon 5 Women's
fields.description: Focus on your goals with these women's Free Metcon 5 trainers from Nike. In a Pale Ivory colourway, these sneaks have a breathable textile upper and inner sleeve for a snug, sock-like fit. They feature a lace fastening to help you stay locked in, a low-cut padded ankle collar for a supportive feel and a moulded heel clip for stability. Underfoot is a soft foam midsole for a smooth ride, whilst Nike Free tech in the forefoot brings a natural flex to your step. With a rubber outsole for traction, they're signed off with the Swoosh to the sidewalls.

fields.name: adidas Originals Gazelle Women's
fields.description: Add a signature style to your rotation with these women's Gazelle trainers from adidas Originals. In an Arctic Fusion colourway, these OG sneaks have a soft suede upper for a premium feel. They feature a tonal lace fastening with a low-cut ankle collar for a snug, secure fit, and sit atop a lightweight cushioned midsole for all-day comfort. With a grippy rubber outsole underfoot, they're finished with a metallic Gazelle wordmark to the sidewalls and the iconic 3-Stripes. Signed off with the legendary Trefoil logo at the tongue and heel.

fields.name: adidas Originals Floral Firebird Track Top
fields.description: Bring a sports heritage style to your everyday 'fits with this women's Floral Firebird Track Top from adidas Originals. In a Black colourway with an all-over floral print, this slim-fit top is made with smooth, lightweight recycled polyester for lasting comfort. It features a full-zip fastening with a stand-up collar for quick coverage, and stretchy ribbing at the cuffs and hem to secure the fit. With front pockets for easy storage, it's finished up with signature 3-Stripes down the sleeves and the iconic Trefoil logo at the chest. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'8" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Jordan Essential T-Shirt
fields.description: Go classic with this women's Essential T-Shirt from Jordan. In a Galactic Jade colourway, this standard fit tee is cut from soft cotton fabric for everyday comfort. It features short sleeves with a ribbed crew neckline and is finished up with embroidered Jordan branding to the chest.

fields.name: JUICY COUTURE Velour Bucket Hat
fields.description: Round off your rotation with a vintage look in this women's Velour Bucket Hat from Juicy Couture. Landing in a Fuchsia Pink colourway, this hat made with a velour fabric that's soft and lightweight for complete comfort. With a 360 degree brim for classic coverage, it's finished with Juicy Couture branding to the front.

fields.name: adidas Hybrid 100 Boxing Gloves
fields.description: Get ready for the ring in these Hybrid 100 Boxing Gloves from adidas. Featuring an ergonomic shape, the gloves are made with PU for toughness and come with hook/loop and elastic strap closure. Land your biggest and best hook in these boxing gloves. The injection mould foam protects and absorbs the impact, with velcro straps for extra security. Finished in a blue and white colourway with a Badge of Sport to the dorsal.

fields.name: Nike Alpha Trainer 5
fields.description: Level up your workout with these men's Alpha Trainer 5 sneakers from Nike. In a Football Grey colourway with University Red accents, these treads have a breathable mesh upper with synthetic skin overlays for added support. They feature a tonal lace fastening with plush padding around the anke for a locked-in fit, and sit atop a light foam midsole with Max Air cushioning underfoot for unbeatable comfort. They have a flat, wide sole for added stability, with an enhanced rubber tread to keep you gripped. With flex grooves in the forefoot for a natural feel, and rubber to wrap the sides, they're signed off with the iconic Swoosh at the sidewalls and signature branding throughout.

fields.name: Nike React Pegasus Trail 4 GORE-TEX
fields.description: Own the elements with these men's React Pegasus Trail 4 GORE-TEX trainers from Nike. In a Deep Jungle and Night Maroon colourway, these off-road runners have a GORE-TEX layer across the lightweight and flexible mesh and synthetic upper to keep your foot dry. They feature a supportive and stretchy ankle collar for extra protection frm debris, while heel and tongue loops offer easy entry. Underfoot, the responsive yet durable Nike React foam midsole sits above a rubber outsole that wraps around the foot for standout traction. Finished off with the signature Swoosh and Nike Trail branding.

fields.name: Nike Miler 1.0 T-Shirt
fields.description: Go further with this men's Miler 1.0 T-Shirt from Nike. In a Smoke Grey colourway, this tee is made with a lightweight and smooth poly fabric for lasting comfort. It features sweat-wicking Dri-FIT tech to keep you cool, and a crew neckline with short sleeves for a classic cut. Signed off with the Swoosh to the chest. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'0" with a 38" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: Nike 3-Pack Trunks
fields.description: When training comes around, stock up on the essentials with this men's 3-Pack Trunks from Nike. Perfect for active days, these trunks are made from stretchy polyester fabric, using sweat-wicking Dri-FIT tech for cool comfort. They have an elasticated waistband that lies flat for an unrestricted fit. Finished off with repeated Nike Swoosh branding. Machine washable. | Please note: For hygiene reasons, underwear cannot be returned.

fields.name: Fred Perry Twin Tipped Polo Shirt
fields.description: Elevate your out-out look with this men's Twin-Tipped Polo Shirt from Fred Perry. In a Black and Navy colourway, this standard fit shirt is cut from soft cotton fabric for total comfort. It features short sleeves with a two-button placket fastening for adjustable coverage, with a spread collar for a classic look. It has ribbed cuffs for a snug feel and is finished up with twin-tipped details and a Laurel Wreath to the chest. Machine washable | Our model is 6'1" with a 39" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: Nike 6-Pack Everyday Cushioned Training Crew Socks
fields.description: Support every stride with this men's 6-Pack Everyday Cushioned Training Socks from Nike. In multiple colourways, these crew-length socks are made from a stretchy and breathable cotton blend for cool comfort. They're equipped with sweat-wicking Dri-FIT tech and feature arch bands for a snug fit. Finished off with varsity-inspired Nike Swoosh branding to the cuff. Machine washable.

fields.name: Under Armour Pants UA Stretch Woven Cargo Pants
fields.description:
The goal with the UA Woven collection was to make the perfect set of warm-ups that keep your muscles ready, work for any sport, and also pack up super-small in your bag, so you can take them anywhere.
 Storm technology repels water without sacrificing breathability
 Lightweight stretch-woven fabric delivers superior comfort and durability
 4-way stretch material moves better in every direction
 Soft, ColdGear knit waistband with internal drawcord
 Open hand pockets and snap-closure cargo pockets
 Encased elastic cuffs

fields.name: Nicce OG Tracksuit
fields.description: Level up your chill-day looks with this men's OG Tracksuit from Nicce. In a Grey colourway, this standard-fit suit is made with a soft cotton-blend fleece for lasting comfort. It features a long-sleeve pullover with a drawstring-adjustable hood to amp up the coverage. It has matching joggers with an elasticated drawcord waistband for a relaxed feel, and pockets for easy storage. With stretchy ribbed trims throughout for a clean, secure fit, it's signed off with tonal Nicce branding at the chest, back and thigh. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'1" with a 39" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: Nike Air Force 1 Low
fields.description: Stand tall in the style stakes with these men's Nike Air Force 1 Lo trainers! An instant icon ever since 1982, the AF1 was Nike's first basketball shoe with a full length Air Sole unit in the midsole. Hugely popular on the hip hop scene, these Nike Air Force 1 trainers are built with a crisp white leather upper for hard-wearing comfort. Sat atop the legendary Air Sole unit for optimum impact protection step after step, pivot points to the outsole deliver smooth movements from the courts to the streets, while the legendary Swoosh finishes things off with authority.

fields.name: adidas Own the Run Leggings
fields.description:
Whether you're hitting the pavement with your community or on your own, there's nothing quite like the joyful rush of a runner's high. One thing's for sure: comfort and support are paramount in maximizing your daily run. Introducing the Own The Run Leggings. Designed for ultimate comfort, they're cut for a flattering tight fit with a drawcord waist that keeps them in place as you stride. Crafted from supportive fabric, sweat-wicking AEROREADY technology will help keep you feeling dry as you put in the kms. When you're in a hurry, ankle zips are a lifesaver, making for easy on and off  even over shoes. Get your run in at any time of day with reflective details that shine in low light, and easily stash your phone and keys in the leg pockets on the go.
 This model is 186 cm and wears a size M. Their chest measures 97 cm and the waist 80 cm.
 Tight fit
 Drawcord on elastic waist
 72% recycled polyester, 28% elastane interlock
 AEROREADY
 Leg pockets
 Reflective details
 Ankle zips

fields.name: Nike 6-Pack Everyday Cushioned Ankle Socks
fields.description: Made for training, this 6-Pack Everyday Cushioned Ankle Socks from Nike keeps feet comfy. In Black colourways, these socks are made from breathable poly fabric with Dri-FIT tech to wick away sweat. They feature a thick terry sole for maximum comfort during footdrills and lifts, as well as a ribbed arch band, which wraps your midfoot for a supportive feel. Finished with the iconic Swoosh logo to the cuff in white. Machine washable.

fields.name: adidas Originals 6 Pack Trefoil Crew Socks
fields.description: Stock up on adidas Originals essentials with this men's 6-Pack Trefoil Crew Socks. In Active Purple, Collegiate Green and Navy, Maroon, Shadow Brown and Wonder White colourways, these crew-cut socks are made from a stretchy, ribbed cotton and recycled poly blend for all-day comfort. With arch supports and reinforced areas to make them last, they're finished off with the Trefoil at the cuff. Machine washable.

fields.name: adidas Originals All Team
fields.description: Take your lace-up rotation to new heights with these All Team sneakers from adidas Originals. In a Collegiate Blue colourway, these sneaks are cut from smooth leather in the upper for a premium feel and lasting wear. They feature a lace fastening to lock you in, with a padded collar for support and textile lining for a snug fit. Underfoot, they sit on a rubber outsole for traction and are finished up with 3-Stripes to the sidewalls and signature Trefoil branding.

fields.name: Nike Knit Gloves
fields.description: Keep things cosy with these Knit Gloves from Nike. In a black colourway, these gloves are made from a a double knit fabric for ultra-warming wear. With grip to the palms, these gloves are finished up with a outline Swoosh. Machine washable.

fields.name: Jordan Airborne Cross Body Bag
fields.description: Secure your smaller essentials with this Airborne Cross Body Bag from Jordan. Coming in a Black colourway, this small-size crossbody is made with hardwearing poly fabric to keep your gear safe. It features a zippered main compartment, and a front pocket for easy organisation. With an adjustable shoulder strap for a custom look, it's finished up with classic Jordan branding to the front. Spot clean.

fields.name: CRUYFF Mosaic
fields.description: Upgrade your kick rotation with these men's Mosaic sneakers from Cruyff. In a Black and Winter White colourway, these sneaks are cut from smooth leather and ripstop mesh in the upper for a durable wear. They feature a lace fastening to lock you in, with a padded collar for support and a stabiliser heel for stability. Underfoot, they sit on a chunky foam midsole for a cushioned step, with a grippy rubber outsole for total traction. Finished up with signature Cruyff branding.

fields.name: Nike Victori Slides
fields.description: Cop a summer essential that can be worn for chilling or hitting the streets with these Victori Slides from Nike. In a Navy colourway, these versatile slides are designed with a comfortable foam sole for cushioning and support while the padded strap and moulded grip on the footbed will keep you locked in with every step. Finshed off with classic Nike Swoosh branding.

fields.name: adidas Originals 3-Pack Crew Socks
fields.description: Update your everyday essentials with this 3-Pack Crew Socks from adidas Originals. Coming in a White colourway, these socks are made with a soft, stretchy cotton blend for lasting comfort. With a stretchy ribbed design for a snug fit, they have a classic crew length and padding underfoot for all-day comfort. Finished with signature Trefoil branding throughout. Machine washable.

fields.name: Nike Everyday Plus Cushioned Crew Socks (3-Pack)
fields.description: Update your daily essentials with this 3-Pack Everyday Plus Cushioned Crew Socks from Nike. In Green, White and Purple colourways, these socks are made with a soft, durable cotton blend with extra stretch for lasting comfort. With a breathable knit construction and Dri-FIT tech to keep you cool, they have plush cushioning underfoot and a tightly-ribbed crew cuff for a secure fit. Finished with contrast Swoosh branding at the side. Machine washable.

fields.name: Nike Strike 1/4 Zip Drill Top
fields.description: Level up your training in this women's Strike 1/4 Zip Drill Top from Nike. In a Hyper Turquoise colourway, this slim-fit top is made with smooth, stretch-woven polyester for lasting comfort. Equipped with Nike's sweat-wicking Dri-FIT tech, it features a quarter zip fastening with a slightly raised collar to adjust your airflow. It as long, streamlined sleeves with thumb holes to secure the fit, and is finished with signature Nike branding to the chest. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'8" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Jordan Air 1 Elevate High Women's
fields.description: Take your game to new heights with these women's Air 1 Elevate High sneakers from Jordan. In a Red Stardust and White colour block design, these reimagined classics have a crisp leather upper for premium style. They feature a perforated toe for cool comfort and a zip fastening at the padded collar for easy on-and-off. Underfoot, the platform cupsole construction has Nike Air tech in the midsole to absorb every stride, while the durable rubber outsole grips your ride. Finished off with Black Swooshes on the sidewalls and the Air Wings outline to the ankle.

fields.name: Nike Air Force 1 Shadow Women's
fields.description: Rep these women's Air Force 1 Shadow trainers from Nike for a basketball-inspired look. Coming in a White colourway with Light Lemon Twist accents, these low-profile sneakers have an upper cut from a smooth but durable leather. They feature a lace fastening to lock you in, a padded ankle for a snug feel, and perforations to the toe for added airflow. Underfoot is a responsive foam midsole that combines with Nike Air cushioning for a super-smooth ride. With a rubber outsole for traction, they're finished with the Swoosh to the sidewalls.

fields.name: adidas Originals Gazelle Bold Women's
fields.description: Turn up the volume when you step out in these women's Gazelle Bold sneakers from adidas Originals. In a White and Core Black colourway, these JD-exclusives have a premium leather upper and synthetic lining. They're sat on a stacked platform midsole to elevate your cushioning and style. With a low-profile rubber outsole for essential grip, these trainers are finished off with the 3-Stripes to the sidewalls and the Trefoil to the tongue. | IE7853

fields.name: Nike Free Run Next Nature Women's
fields.description: Go the distance in these women's Free Run Next Nature sneakers from Nike. In a Guava Ice colourway with Vivid Sulfur accents, these runners have a soft, stretchy Flyknit upper for a sock-like feel. They have a tonal lace fastening with a snug ankle collar to lock you in, and sit atop an ultra-lightweight foam midsole for supreme comfort as you move. They have a Nike Grind rubber outsole with flex grooves for grippy traction, and are finished up with a signature Swoosh to the sidewalls.

fields.name: Under Armour UA Tech Twist 1/2 Zip Top
fields.description: Feel unrestricted every time you train in this women's UA Tech Twist 1/2 Zip Top from Under Armour. In a Water and White all over twist effect, this stretchy top is made from smooth UA Tech fabric for cool, sweat-wicking comfort. It features a half zip fastening, raglan sleeves and a stand-up collar. Finished off with reflective Under Armour logos printed to the chest and nape. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'7" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Nike Club Futura Cap
fields.description: Stay cool on the streets with this Club Futura Cap from Nike. Dropping in a Black colourway, this lightweight cap is made from breathable poly fabric, paired with sweat-wicking Dri-FIT tech and lined panels for total comfort. It has an adjustable strap to the back for the perfect fit, while the curved bill adds essential coverage. Finished with a metallic Nike Futura badge to the front. Hand wash.

fields.name: Nike Running Headband & Gloves Set
fields.description: On cold weather runs, make sure you're prepared with this women's Essential Running Headband & Gloves Set from Nike. In a black colourway, the headband fits over your ears for warmth, and is made from smooth poly fabric with Dri-FIT to wick away excess sweat. The gloves have touchscreen tips so you can use your phone, as well as a snug cuff to lock in heat. Both are finished with Nike Swoosh branding.

fields.name: UGG Sheepskin Gloves
fields.description: Beat the chilly temps with these women's Sheepskin Gloves from UGG. In a Chestnut colourway, these gloves are cut from smooth leather with a cosy sheepskin lining for a snug feel. They have fur trim for extra warmth and are finished up with signature UGG branding. Hand wash.

fields.name: The North Face Logo Box Cuffed Beanie
fields.description: Stand out on frosty days with this Logo Box Cuffed Beanie from The North Face. In a Pikes Purple colourway, this winter-ready hat is made from stretchy ribbed acrylic knit fabric for a snug feel and lasting warmth and comfort. It has an adjustable cuff for the perfect fit. Finished off with an embroidered TNF box logo to the front. Hand wash.

fields.name: The North Face Logo Box Cuffed Beanie
fields.description: Brighten up your 'fits this season when you pull on this Logo Box Cuffed Beanie from The North Face. In a Persian Orange colourway, this snug-fit beanier has an adjustable cuff for a versatile wear. It's made from ultra-soft and cosy acrylic knit fabric for lasting comfort. Finished with a contrasting TNF box logo stamped to the front. Hand wash.

fields.name: Under Armour Play Up Shorts
fields.description:
Everyone needs a go-to pair of shorts. With side hand pockets and a soft, smooth waistbandthese womens training shorts are it.
 Soft, lightweight knit construction delivers superior comfort breathability
 Material wicks sweat dries really fast
 Updated exposed elastic printed waistband

fields.name: adidas Originals Ribbed Cycle Shorts
fields.description: Cop heat that's exclusive to JD with these women's Essential Ribbed Cycle Shorts from adidas Originals. Coming in an Easy Orange colourway, these tight-fit shorts are cut from a soft and stretchy blended fabric that delivers max' comfort. They feature an elastic waistband for a snug, supportive feel and are finished up with the Trefoil to the thigh. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'8" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Under Armour Fly By 2.0 Short
fields.description:
When it comes to these shorts, we thought of everything: strategic mesh, a key pocket, and reflective hits. So, all youll be thinking about is going faster, longer.
 Lightweight woven fabric delivers superior comfort durability
 Material wicks sweat dries really fast
 Built-in brief for enhanced coverage

fields.name: Nike Training One 3" Shorts
fields.description: Get moving in style with these women's Training One 3" Shorts from Nike. In a Light Fusion Red colourway, these workout shorts are cut from ultra-soft and lighweight woven fabric for comfort, while Dri-FIT tech wicks sweat from the skin. They have a mid-rise elasticated waistband and a stretchy mesh brief liner, while the envelope waistband pocket secures your phone in place. Finished with a reflective Swoosh to the left leg. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'9" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Emporio Armani EA7 Overhead Hoodie Tape Tracksuit
fields.description: Elevate your off-duty style with this women's Overhead Hoodie Tape Tracksuit from Emporio Armani EA7. In a JD-exclusive Purple colourway, this matching set has a pullover hoodie with a drawcord-adjustable hood, ribbed trims and dropped shoulders for a roomy feel. The joggers feature a drawcord tie at the waistband for custom comfort, along with cuffed ankles and open-hand side pockets. Made from a soft and stretchy cotton blend for a plush feel, this suit is finished up with taped EA7 branding down the sleeve and leg. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'5" and wears a size small.

fields.name: The North Face Logo Padded Gilet
fields.description: Take the edge off on cooler days with this women's Logo Hooded Padded Gilet from The North Face. In a Black colourway, this standard fit, JD-exclusive gilet is cut from smooth, water-resistant polyester for a dry, comfy wear. It features a full-zip fastening, funnel collar and hood for custom coverage, with side pockets for your essentials. Finished up with Dome branding to the chest and reverse shoulder. Machine washable | Our model is 5'5" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Nike Training Pro Shine Tank Top
fields.description: Focus on your goals with this women's Training Pro Shine Tank Top fom Nike. In a Black colourway, this slim fit top is cut from light, stretchy fabric for a flexible feel. It features armholes with a crew neckline and an elasticated hem for a secure fit. It's equipped with Dri-FIT tech to remvoe sweat and is finished up with Nike Pro branding. Machine washable | Our model is 5'8" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Nike Training Pro Shine Tank Top
fields.description: Put in a big workout in comfort with this women's Training Pro Shine Tank Top from Nike. In a Deep Jungle colourway, this slim fit top is cut from smooth, stretchy poly fabric for total comfort. It features arm holes and a high neckline for coverage, with built-in Dri-FIT tech to remove sweat. It has an elasticated hem for a secure fit and is finished up with a Swoosh to the chest and Nike Pro branding to the binding. Machine washable | Our model is 5'8" and wears a size small.

fields.name: Vans Knu Skool Women's
fields.description: '90s style gets redefined with these women's Knu Skool sneakers from Vans. In an Ivy Green colourway, these oversized trainers have a durable rough suede upper. They feature a puffy tongue and ankle collar for plush cushioning, while the heel pull and thick laces offer easy entry. Underfoot, the classic sole cushions your ride and grips every step from the rubber Waffle tread. Signed off with a 3D moulded Sidestripe in White.

fields.name: Nike Academy T-Shirt
fields.description: Get set to train in this women's Academy T-Shirt from Nike. In a Midnight Navy colourway, this regular-fit tee is cut from a super-smooth, lightweight polyester fabric for lasting comfort. It's crafted with sweat-wicking Dri-FIT technology, and features a classic crew neckline and short sleeves for an easy feel. Signed off with Nike's iconic Swoosh to the chest. Machine washable.

fields.name: PE Nation Jump Colour Block Tights
fields.description: Support your training goals with these women's Jump Colour Block Tights from P.E Nation. In a Black colourway with Pink and Yellow panels, these JD-exclusive training leggings have a high-rise elasticated waistband that sits flat for total comfort when you squat. They're made from stretchy recycled nylon fabric for a durable and breathable feel. Finished off with signature P.E Nation branding. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'6" and wears a size small.

fields.name: adidas Badge of Sport 3-Stripes Tracksuit
fields.description: Match up classic adidas style with this men's Badge Of Sport 3-Stripes Tracksuit from adidas. In a Black colourway, this regular-fit set is made from smooth recycled polyester fabric. The full zip track top has a mock collar and ribbed trims, while the pants feature a drawcord-adjustable waistband and cuffed ankles. With side pockets to stash your essentials, it's finished with contrasting 3-Stripes and the Sportswear logo to the chest and leg. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'0" with a 37" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: Fred Perry Twin Tipped Half Zip Sweatshirt
fields.description: Refresh your layers in premium style with this men's Twin Tipped Half Zip Sweatshirt from Fred Perry. In a Sky Blue colourway, this standard fit top is cut from soft fleece fabric for total comfort. It features a half-zip fastening and long sleeves, with ribbed trims for a snug fit. Finished up with twin-tipped detailing to the cuffs, with a Laurel Wreath to the chest. Machine washable | Our model is 6'1" with a 39" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: New Balance Polar 1/4 Zip Fleece
fields.description: Freshen up your layers with this men's Polar 1/4 Zip Fleece from New Balance. Exclusive to JD, this standard-fit fleece is crafted with a super-soft and warm poly fabric for lasting comfort. It features a 1/4 zip fastening with a stand-up collar for personalised coverage, and has ribbed cuffs to elevate the fit. Signed off with New Balance branding to the chest. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'10" with a 38" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: adidas Energize Overhead Hoodie
fields.description: Bring a laidback vibe with this men's Energize Overhead Hoodie from adidas. In a Stone colourway, this JD-exclusive hoodie is cut from soft fleece fabric that partly includes recycled polyester. It features a pullover, adjustable hood for custom coverge, with ribbed trims for a secure fit and a kangaroo pouch for easy storage. Finished up with 3-Stripes to the sleeves and a Badge of Sport to the chest. Machine washable | Our model is 6'0" with a 40" chest and wears a size medium. | IT0208

fields.name: Nike Air Max 1/4 Zip Fleece Hoodie
fields.description: Pick up a street-ready layer with this men's Air Max 1/4 Zip Fleece Hoodie from Nike, exclusive to JD. In a Cool Grey colourway, this regular-fit hoodie is made with a smooth, lightweight polyester fleece for lasting comfort. Equipped with Therma-FIT tech to keep you warm on colder days, it features a quarter zip fastening with an adjustable hood. It has a large zipped pouch up front for quick and easy storage, with stretchy ribbed trims to secure the fit. Finished with signature Nike Air Maz branding throughout. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'0" with a 37" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: Nike Core T-Shirt
fields.description: Freshen up your staple cuts with this men's Core T-Shirt from Nike. In a Polar colourway, this regular-fit tee is made with soft, lightweight cotton for easy comfort. It features a ribbed crew neckline and short sleeves for a classic look, and is finished with an embroidered Nike logo at the chest. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'11.5" with a 36" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: Nike Miler 1.0 T-Shirt
fields.description: Level up your fitness 'fits with this men's Miler 1.0 T-Shirt from Nike. This tee comes in a Chile Red colourway and is cut from a lightweight and smooth poly fabric for easy wear as you train. It features sweat-wicking Dri-FIT tech for cool comfort, and a crew neckline with short sleeves for a classic look. Signed off with the Swoosh to the chest. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'0" with a 38.5" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: Nike 3-Pack Trunks
fields.description: Refresh your everyday staples with this men's 3-Pack Trunks from Nike. Cut from soft, lightweight fabric with added stretch for essential comfort, these slim-fit trunks come in Blue, Grey and Black colourways. Each featuring a woven elasticated waistband, they're finished up with contrasting Nike branded graphics around the waist. Machine washable. | Please note: for hygiene purposes, underwear cannot be returned.

fields.name: adidas Badge of Sport Backpack
fields.description: Carry your essentials wherever you go with this Badge of Sport Backpack from adidas. In a black colourway, this bag is made from durable, recycled poly fabric. It features a secure zip fastening and opens to reveal a spacious main compartment with an internal slip pocket. With a zip pocket to the front for quick-access storage, this backpack has a single grab handle and dual, adjustable backpack straps so you can carry it in comfort. It's finished with a white Badge of Sport logo stamped to the front.|HE9697

fields.name: Nike F.C. Neck Warmer Snood
fields.description: Block out the cold with this F.C. Neck Warmer Snood from Nike. Coming in a Black colourway, this snood is made from a soft, stretchy poly fabric that's equipped with sweat-wicking Dri-FIT tech so you can focus on your game. In a standard-fit for relaxed and comfy wear, it's signed off with the famous Swoosh to the front. Machine washable.

fields.name: Nike Brasilia Bag
fields.description: Keep organised with this Brasilia Bag from Nike. In a Black colourway, this bag is made from a light and durable poly fabric that uses at least 50% recycled material. It features a main zippered compartment, a zippered inner compartment to stash sweaty clothes whilst the coated bottom offers lasting wear. With a detachable shoulder strap for custom comfort, it's signed off with the Swoosh to the front. Spot clean. (H: 25.4cm x W: 25.4cm x D: 38.1cm).

fields.name: Nike Air Max 95
fields.description: Step to the streets in these men's Air Max 95 sneakers from Nike. In a JD-exclusive Iron Grey and Hyper Turquoise colourway, these treads have a mixed-material upper with breathable mesh, and real and synthetic leather for lasting wear. Featuring stitched panels to make the iconic wavy design, they have a secure lace closure and padding around the ankle collar for a locked-in fit. With roots in performance running, they have visible Air cushioning underfoot for unbeatable comfort, with flex grooves through the midsole for a natural feel. They have a grippy rubber outsole for traction, and are signed off with classic Swoosh branding throughout.

fields.name: adidas Originals AS 520
fields.description: '80s style gets a modern update with these men's AS 520 trainers from adidas Originals. In a Core Black colourway with Off White accents, these JD-exclusive kicks have a premium suede and leather upper. They feature a synthetic lining, while the streamlined foam midsole delivers lightweight cushioning. With a Trefoil tread for retro-inspired grip, these trainers are finished off with the 3-Stripes to the sidewalls.

fields.name: Nike Air Max Track Pants
fields.description: Keep your street-style on point with these men's Air Max Track Pants from Nike. In a Cool Grey colourway, these standard fit pants are cut from smooth polyester fabric for total comfort. They feature an elasticated, drawcord waistband for a relaxed fit, with ribbed cuffs for a snug feel and zip-up side pockets for secure storage. They're equipped with Therma-FIT tech to keep you toasty on chilly days and are finished up with classic Air Max branding to the leg. Machine washable | Our model wears a size medium.

fields.name: HUGO Erato Overshirt
fields.description: Freshen up your weekend essentials with this men's Erato Overshirt from HUGO. In a Black colourway, this standard-fit shirt is made with soft, durable cotton twill for lasting comfort. It features a full-length button-down fastening with a flat spread collar, and long sleeves with buttoned cuffs to secure the fit. It has a classic curved hem, and two chest pockets for easy storage. Signed off with the iconic HUGO Red patch at the chest. Machine washable. | Our model is 6'1" with a 39" chest and wears a size medium.

fields.name: Nike Just Do It Fuel Jug 64oz
fields.description: From long runs to big gym sessions, stay hydrated with this Just Do It Fuel Jug 64oz from Nike. In a black colourway, this large bottle is made from lightweight yet durable plastic and has an adjustable handle for easy carry to and from training. It features space to write your name, as well as textured hand grips for a comfy fit. With a simple cap top that shuts securely when not in use, this bottle is finished off with contrasting 'Just Do It' branding to the side.

fields.name: Nike Big Mouth Water Bottle 22oz
fields.description: Hold more water in this Nike Big Mouth Water Bottle 22oz. Built with a durable pink plastic construction which features squeezable design with push-pull spout for easy drinking. Not just easy to use, but also easy to wash in a dishwasher. Finished with a white Swoosh.

fields.name: adidas Manchester United FC 2023 Water Bottle
fields.description: Stay hydrated on the pitch with this Manchester United FC 2023 Water Bottle from adidas. In a Black colourway, this 750ml bottle is made from dishwasher-safe polyethylene, with an ergonomic design for a comfy feel in the hand. Featuring a pull spout and screw cap for easy refills, this bottle is finished off with contrasting adidas branding and the United crest.

fields.name: adidas Hybrid 100 Boxing Gloves
fields.description: Make sure you're getting peak performance when you step through the ropes with these Hybrid 100 Boxing Gloves from adidas. In a red colourway with white and black accents, these boxing gloves are made with durable poly and padded foam for essential cushioning. Coming with a Velcro strap for a locked-in fit, these boxing gloves are finished with white adidas branding to the back for the hands.

fields.name: adidas Real Madrid CF 2023 Water Bottle
fields.description: Stay hydrated as you train with this Real Madrid CF 2023 Water Bottle from adidas. In a White colourway, this bottle is made from durable polyethylene and can hold up to 750ml of water. It features a twist cap for easy refill, with a pull-up spout to drink from. Finished up with the Real Madrid crest and Badge of Sport logo.

fields.name: Nike Academy Tracksuit
fields.description: Suit up in style with a set designed for warming up and looking cool. The zip-up jacket and adjustable trousers allow for versatile styling. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

fields.name: adidas 3-Stripes Essential Tracksuit
fields.description: Freshen up your laidback 'fits with this women's 3-Stripes Essential Tracksuit from adidas. In a Better Scarlet colourway, this slim-fit set is made with smooth recycled poly fabric for lasting comfort. It features a long-sleeve track top with a full-zip fastening and a ribbed bomber collar for a classic look. The matching track pants have an elasticated waistband with a drawcord, while stretchy ribbed trims throughout secure the fit. With zipped pockets for quick storage, it's signed off with adidas' iconic 3-Stripes down the sides and signature Badge of Sport branding. Machine washable. | Our model is 5'10" and wears a size small.
